ForwardX11      yes
ForwardX11Trusted yes
TCPKeepAlive    yes

ControlMaster auto
ControlPath /tmp/ssh_mux_%h_%p_%r 
ServerAliveInterval 30
ServerAliveCountMax 10

host ukmx1 usmx6 usmx7 usmx8
    user admin

